body:
@rlabbe just a quick comment... You could generate individual .tex file of all your notebooks using nbconvert with a custom template (to remove the document class, preamble, begin document, etc.).
Later create a master tex document which inputs all these individual files and takes care of the toc. 
This a common way to structure large documents in latex, see e.g. [this wiki](http://en.wikibooks.org/wiki/LaTeX/Modular_Documents)
